## 3. High-Assurance Architectural Goals & Target Criteria

By moving verification away from heavy runtime wrappers and replacing them with static validation proofs and single-cycle bitmask gates, LogicN achieves three major architectural milestones.

### Goal A: Native Hardware Speed Execution

**Target Criteria:** Code blocks compile and run without runtime performance penalties or active out-of-band monitoring loops.

```
